parse

public HashGraph parse(java.lang.String fileName)
                throws java.io.IOException
parse fileName, after creating a Tokeniser for it

If fileName ends in ".gz" a gzip input stream is created, otherwise a normal input stream is created for the Tokeniser

Parameters:
fileName - the dictionary to parse
Returns:
the corresponding ontology, as a HashGraph
Throws:
java.io.IOException - on an IO error
